728127f-a.title: Queens: Union Turnpike - 138th Street
728127f-a.text:
Union Turnpike, south side (foreground), at 138th Street (formerly Hoffman Ave.), showing two frame houses.  View No. 1 shows the S.E. corner and the Guesthouse of Arman Lazarus, a road house.  In View No. 2, at the S.W. corner, is another guesthouse known as the Gasthaus zeun Armen Teufel.

April 1929.
View 2: August 1925.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
